Fix the UNSAFE order processor below. It has race conditions in orderCount and totalRevenue. 10 threads each process 5 orders of ₹1000. Expected: count=50, revenue=₹50000.

```java
// UNSAFE — has race conditions:
class OrderProcessor {
    int orderCount = 0;
    double totalRevenue = 0.0;
    void processOrder(double amount) {
        orderCount++;
        totalRevenue += amount;
    }
}
```

Expected output:
Order count: 50
Total revenue: ₹50000.00

